PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780071066
OL,3,CMoment Blue Origin rocket explodes
OL,4,Cinto fireball during test launch
OL,6,FHomes nearby shook at around 9pm local
OL,7,Ftime on Thursday, with photos and
OL,8,Ffootage of the sky being lit up by an
OL,9,Forange fireball quickly flooding
OL,10,Fsocial media.
OL,12,FBlue Origin said its New Glenn rocket
OL,13,Fexploded during an engine-firing test.
OL,14,FThe rocket was supposed to blast off
OL,15,Fnext week with internet satellites
OL,16,Fthat are part of the Amazon Leo
OL,17,Fconstellation in orbit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780071066
OL,3,CMoment Blue Origin rocket explodes
OL,4,Cinto fireball during test launch
OL,6,F"It's too early to know the root
OL,7,Fcause, but we're already working to
OL,8,Ffind it," Bezos said via X. "Very
OL,9,Frough day, but we'll rebuild whatever
OL,10,Fneeds rebuilding and get back to
OL,11,Fflying. It's worth it."
OL,13,FThe massive New Glenn was grounded in
OL,14,FApril after it left a satellite in the
OL,15,Fwrong orbit due to engine failure.
OL,17,FIt was only the third flight of the
OL,18,Frocket that Blue Origin intends to use
OL,19,Fto launch landers to the moon for Nasa
OL,20,Fincluding the landers that will take
OL,21,Fastronauts to the lunar surface.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
