PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780071066
OL,3,CMoment Blue Origin rocket explodes
OL,4,Cinto fireball during test launch
OL,6,FThe company had been on track to
OL,7,Flaunch a prototype lunar lander to the
OL,8,Fmoon on a flight test this autumn.
OL,10,FEarlier this week, the space agency
OL,11,Fawarded Blue Origin a contract worth
OL,12,Fhundreds of millions of dollars to
OL,13,Flaunch a pair of moon buggies in the
OL,14,Fnext few years as part of the Artemis
OL,15,Fprogramme.
OL,17,F"Spaceflight is unforgiving, and
OL,18,Fdeveloping new heavy-lift launch
OL,19,Fcapability is extraordinarily
OL,20,Fdifficult," Nasa administrator Jared
OL,21,FIsaacman said via X.
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
