PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780071066
OL,3,CMoment Blue Origin rocket explodes
OL,4,Cinto fireball during test launch
OL,6,FHe promised to provide information on
OL,7,Fany impacts to the Artemis programme,
OL,8,Fincluding the moon base that he
OL,9,Frecently outlined.
OL,11,FUnited States Space Force officials
OL,12,Fsaid the explosion would not affect
OL,13,Fupcoming launches by other companies
OL,14,Ffrom other pads.
OL,16,FUnited Launch Alliance's Atlas V
OL,17,Frocket is due to blast off Friday
OL,18,Fnight with a batch of Amazon Leo
OL,19,Fsatellites, the same kind that this
OL,20,Frocket was supposed to take up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
