PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780071066
OL,3,CMoment Blue Origin rocket explodes
OL,4,Cinto fireball during test launch
OL,6,FSpaceX's Elon Musk, who's had his own
OL,7,Fshare of rocket explosions, offered
OL,8,Fhis condolences, writing on X: "Sorry
OL,9,Fto see this, I hope you recover
OL,10,Fquickly."
OL,12,FTowering at 321 feet, New Glenn made
OL,13,Fits debut in 2025.
OL,15,FIt is named after John Glenn, the
OL,16,Ffirst American to orbit Earth, and is
OL,17,Flarger and more powerful than Blue
OL,18,FOrigin's New Shepard rockets that have
OL,19,Fcarried tourists to the fringes of
OL,20,Fspace from Texas.
OL,26,@pD@`OUrD@IO]
